.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, traveling, singing, board-games, magic-tricks
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, drama, superhero, crime, time-travel
There 5 different types of food: corn, nectarine, radish, watermelon, peas
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different games are played: bridge, domino, snooker, mah-jongg, scrabble

1. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is camping
2. the person watching drama movies is the person playing bridge
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is traveling
4. the person watching superhero movies is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is to the right of the person who's hobby is singing
6. the person eating corn is the person playing scrabble
7. the person eating nectarine is the person who's hobby is board-games
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person watching crime movies is on the far left
10. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person playing domino
11. the person eating nectarine is to the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg
12. the person eating watermelon is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person watching time-travel movies is the person eating peas
14. the person watching crime movies is to the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Movie-Genre	|   crime	|    superhero	|     musical	|    drama	|    time-travel	|
| Hobby		|    board-games	|      magic-tricks	|      camping	|     singing	|     traveling	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Food		|     nectarine	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| watermelon	|   parliament	|
| Game		|     domino	|     mah-jongg	|     scrabble	|     bridge	|     snooker	|
